      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FARMOR MYSTIC (3) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing second and beaten 2 lengths (24.08) behind Bonito at this track. Sure to be about the mark. VOCIFEROUS (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (24.41) at this track behind Velocity Ziggy in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature again. UNTAMED ENVY (7) broke a string of placings finishing in the money three on end before a last start fourth (24.44) at this track. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Shapes as one to consider. LOUCA (5) was unplaced here when making debut but gets his chance to atone.",
